import { Box, Button, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import React from 'react'

const SecondPage = () => {
    return (
        <Box sx={{ marginTop: '50px' }}>
            <Box sx={{ display: 'flex', flexDirection: 'row', width: "100%", }}>
                <Typography variant='h6' sx={{ fontSize: '20px', fontWeight: 'bold' }}>Popular Health Checkup Packages</Typography>
                <Button variant='outlined' color='#2CCE6C' sx={{ color: '#2CCE6C', textTransform: 'capitalize' }}>Compare Packages</Button>
                <Button variant='outlined' color='#2CCE6C' sx={{ color: '#2CCE6C', textTransform: 'capitalize' }}>Create Your Package</Button>
                <Button variant='outlined' color='#2CCE6C' sx={{ color: '#2CCE6C', textTransform: 'capitalize' }}>View All Package</Button>
            </Box>

        </Box>
    )
}

export default SecondPage
